Malcha bade noka raayi{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Melimi vendi raajyaalanu iththadi inupa
Raajyaadhulanu ee raayi ye naluga
Gottunu Cheththa valene{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Priyudaa vinthaina ee raayi perigi
Bhooloka manthaaye prabhu kristuni
Vintha saarvathrika sangha mide{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Aa raajyamunu choochu bhaagyam
Aa raajyamulo cheredi bhaagyam
Anubhavimpa nagunu parishudda prajalake{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Ee suhrudaya shuddi neeku kristu prabhuve
Kaluga cheyun ye saatiyuleni
Ee shuddi nondumu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Manakitchina aahwaanambunaku thana
